  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "At the moment `get_attestation_participants` has a single `assert`:\r\n\r\n> assert len(participation_bitfield) == ceil_div8(len(shard_committee.committee))\r\n\r\nWe also need to check that:\r\n\r\n* `participation_bitfield` is not all zero (`bls_verify` isn't defined when the pubkey is 0â€”it would actually be natural to have it return `True`.)\r\n* If `len(shard_committee.committee) % 8 != 0` the unused bits should be set to 0.\r\n\r\nSomething similar should be done for `custody_bitfield`.",
